%% ThunderaFit — billing flow (complementary diagram)
%% Stripe Checkout + webhook. See src/billing/AGENTS.md for the tier-gating
%% pattern and BILLING_SETUP.md for env/product setup. Billing owns no
%% Prisma tables — all state lives on auth's User (planoAssinatura,
%% stripeCustomerId, stripeSubscriptionId).

sequenceDiagram
    participant C as "Client (frontend)"
    participant API as "Fastify (src/billing)"
    participant Stripe
    participant DB as "Postgres (User, in src/auth)"

    C->>API: POST /api/billing/checkout (tier: BASE|PLUS, interval)
    API->>Stripe: create Checkout Session (metadata.tier)
    Stripe-->>C: redirect to hosted Checkout page
    C->>Stripe: pays

    Stripe->>API: webhook: checkout.session.completed (signed, raw body)
    API->>API: verify signature (rawBody stashed by app.ts content-type parser)
    API->>DB: set stripeCustomerId, stripeSubscriptionId, planoAssinatura = tier

    Note over Stripe,API: Later — plan change via customer portal

    Stripe->>API: webhook: customer.subscription.updated
    API->>API: map price.id -> tier (unknown price -> BASE, never guessed PLUS)
    API->>DB: update planoAssinatura

    Stripe->>API: webhook: customer.subscription.deleted
    API->>DB: planoAssinatura = FREE, availableForNewStudents = false

    Note over API: STRIPE_* env unset -> checkout/webhook inert,<br/>rest of the app works normally (billing is opt-in infra)
